block.command_block.394.command.2:
Collect diamonds to earn points!
Items spawned per player:
 - Diamonds, worth 1 point, spawn every 0.5 seconds.
 - Diamond Blocks, worth 3 points, spawn every 3 seconds.
 - 1 Diamond Statue spawns every 30 seconds, and will spawn additional diamond blocks at its position every 3 seconds. Statues despawn after 20 seconds.
First player to 250 points wins!
block.command_block.395.command.2:
Use your Loyalty III tridents to kill the zombies!
Enemies spawned per player:
 - Zombie, worth 1 point, spawns every 2.5 seconds.
First player to 50 points wins!
block.command_block.396.command.2:
Use your Riptide III trident to kill enemies!
Enemies spawned per player:
 - Drowned, worth 1 point, spawns every 5 seconds.
 - Guardian, worth 2 points, spawns every 10 seconds.
 - Elder Guardian, worth 5 points, spawns every 20 seconds.
First player to 50 points wins!
block.command_block.397.command.2:
Don't fall in the lava! Use knockback sticks to knock other players into the lava!
 - At the beginning of each round you have 5 seconds until the floor starts to turn to lava.
 - Parts of the floor will turn orange, then red as a warning, then turn to lava for 8 seconds.
The player with the least amount of deaths after 10 rounds wins.
block.command_block.398.command.1: Guess the Pixel Art Full Details
block.command_block.398.command.2:
In each round:
 - Pixel art is slowly drawn on the canvas layer by layer.
 - It takes 30 seconds for the pixel art to be completed.
 - Players have 60 seconds to guess by renaming paper.
 - Players earn more points for guessing first.
The player with the most amount of points after 10 rounds wins!
block.command_block.399.command.2:
Read each question then stand on the green platform for 'True' or the red platform for 'False'.
 - You have 15 seconds to choose an answer for each question.
 - A wall will appear to separate both platforms and the correct answer will be announced.
The player with the most amount of points after 10 questions wins.
block.command_block.400.command.2:
Shoot laser beams by right-clicking the laser gun!
 - One vex per player spawns every 3 seconds.
 - Vexes drop Vex Essence when killed.
The first player to collect 50 Vex Essence wins the game.
block.command_block.401.command.2:
On the wall a pattern will rise up.
When a block reaches the light blue line you must perform a correct action to score a point:
 - Arrows: Move to the pressure plate in that direction
 - Pink concrete: Sneak
 - Blue concrete: Jump
Each game lasts for two minutes. The player who attains the highest score wins.
block.command_block.402.command.1: King of the Dance Floor Full Details
block.command_block.402.command.2:
- Stand on the dance floor in the middle of the arena to gain points!
 - Use knockback sticks to knock other players off the dance floor!
The first player to reach 50 points wins the game.
block.command_block.403.command.2:
In each round:
 - A random beacon color using two glass colors is selected for the central beacon.
 - Players have 60 seconds to mix two correct colors for their beacon by pushing their buttons.
 - Press the 'Confirm' button to see if you are correct. If correct a message will display in chat.
 - Players earn more points for guessing first.
The player with the most amount of points after 10 rounds wins.
block.command_block.404.command.2:
At the beginning choose a map and then each player must choose one of eight colors to be their paint color.
 - Floor is painted in a 3x3 square underneath your feet.
 - You can paint over other players' paint.
The player with the most blocks painted after 60 seconds wins.

dance.functions.dance.intro.17: There are 11 different fun minigames to play on the dance floor! Many can be played on your own, but most are much more fun with friends!
dance.functions.dance.intro.19: You will earn Dance Credits from playing minigames, and you can spend them on various items in the shop!
dance.functions.dance.intro.23: That is all. We hope you enjoy our map and have fun dancing and playing minigames!
dance.functions.dance.player_effect.1: has voted to end the game!
dance.functions.dance.dj.alex.3: ] Don't have anything to say, just jam my records!
dance.functions.dance.dj.alex.6: ] How about Far? That's a nice romantic tune!
dance.functions.dance.dj.alex.9: ] Not a lot of Minecraft music is actually very danceable, I must say...
dance.functions.dance.dj.assassin.9: ] One of the disco balls looks familiar...
dance.functions.dance.dj.assassin.12: ] I never understand why people dance. There's so many other things to do in this world!
dance.functions.dance.dj.blaze.3: ] I would be dancing too but I've got no body to go with.
dance.functions.dance.dj.blaze.12: ] I like the flame dance floor the best.
dance.functions.dance.dj.blaze.15: ] I'm trying very hard not to set off the smoke alarm!
dance.functions.dance.dj.cavinator1.9: ] I need to get the flashing lights on a command block for some effects...
dance.functions.dance.dj.cemrek.9: ] This is the most amazing dance experience ever!!
dance.functions.dance.dj.creeper.6: ] I hate TNT! It explodes louder than me!
dance.functions.dance.dj.creeper.9: ] What ya crying for, did somebody break your diamond sword?
dance.functions.dance.dj.creeper.12: ] That's a very nice dance partner you've got there... it would be a shame if anything were to happen to them... ssss...
dance.functions.dance.dj.creeper.15: ] Me and the iron golem are best buds, believe it or not!
dance.functions.dance.dj.disco_man.3: ] They need to add proper dancing to Minecraft!
dance.functions.dance.dj.disco_man.9: ] Hit those space bars over and over!
dance.functions.dance.dj.disco_man.12: ] Swivel your mouse like nobody's business!
dance.functions.dance.dj.disco_man.15: ] Tell your partner how much they mean to you!
dance.functions.dance.dj.enderman.3: ] You don't want to mess with the endermen!
dance.functions.dance.dj.enderman.9: ] No, no, no, no, no, no, nooo!
dance.functions.dance.dj.enderman.12: ] Apparently I'm too tall to dance with anyone...
dance.functions.dance.dj.enderman.15: ] Anyone know where the toilets are...?
dance.functions.dance.dj.ender_dragon.3: ] Do you have any idea how many times I've been dumped because they thought I had bad breath?
dance.functions.dance.dj.ender_dragon.6: ] Yes, I look a little small! I've been losing weight!
dance.functions.dance.dj.ender_dragon.9: ] Tomorrow night I'll bring in some ender crystals to create some fancy effects for the dance floor!
dance.functions.dance.dj.evoker.3: ] I shall use my magic spells to create the effects on the dance floor!
dance.functions.dance.dj.evoker.6: ] If you won't dance my vexes will dance for you!
dance.functions.dance.dj.ghast.3: ] Come, I shall sing some songs for you!
dance.functions.dance.dj.ghast.9: ] Remember, it's what's on the inside that counts!
dance.functions.dance.dj.ghast.15: ] My tentacles shall embrace you as we dance!
dance.functions.dance.dj.guardian.3: ] Who needs laser lights when you've got me?
dance.functions.dance.dj.guardian.6: ] I tried asking a beautiful tropical fish out once but she was dating a pufferfish... his spines were not nearly as impressive as mine >:(
dance.functions.dance.dj.guardian.12: ] The red lasers in the Laser Show game are cheap knock-offs compared to what I have!
dance.functions.dance.dj.guardian.15: ] Elder Guardians are terrible DJs. They keep cursing everyone.
dance.functions.dance.dj.herobrine.3: ] Anyone want to dance with me...?
dance.functions.dance.dj.herobrine.6: ] Oh yeah, I totally have so many fangirls. I have girls leaping on me every day!
dance.functions.dance.dj.iron_golem.3: ] It's time for some heavy metal!
dance.functions.dance.dj.iron_golem.9: ] I throw my hands up in the air sometimes...
dance.functions.dance.dj.llama.12: ] I will spit at anyone who touches my DJ set!
dance.functions.dance.dj.shulker.3: ] Anyone want me to turn off the gravity? You could pull off some pretty sick dance moves!
dance.functions.dance.dj.shulker.6: ] I'm a huuge introvert... always hiding in my shell...
dance.functions.dance.dj.shulker.9: ] So what if I like the girly dance floor? That's a stupid name in my opinion...
dance.functions.dance.dj.shulker.12: ] I wish I could make my projectiles do more than just chase after people...
dance.functions.dance.dj.shulker.15: ] I don't care that I can't dance. I like watching other people dance.
dance.functions.dance.dj.skeleton.6: ] It's time to throw your bones around!
dance.functions.dance.dj.skeleton.9: ] Come on, I want to see bones jiggling!
dance.functions.dance.dj.skeleton.12: ] What's that? Yes, I am totally Michael Jackson's skeleton!
dance.functions.dance.dj.slime.9: ] I can keep up the beat. It sounds squishy through.
dance.functions.dance.dj.slime.12: ] Nobody ever wanted to dance with me. They said I'm too clingy.
dance.functions.dance.dj.slime.15: ] I like hopping up and down!
dance.functions.dance.dj.snow_golem.3: ] Do you want to build a snowman?
dance.functions.dance.dj.snow_golem.6: ] Let it go! Let it go!
dance.functions.dance.dj.snow_golem.9: ] I don't know why, but I always love the idea of summer!
dance.functions.dance.dj.snow_golem.12: ] Jingle bells, jingle bells, jingle all the way!
dance.functions.dance.dj.snow_golem.15: ] We wish you a merry christmas and a happy new year!
dance.functions.dance.dj.steve.15: ] Gotta keep watching my back out here.
dance.functions.dance.dj.villager.9: ] Anyone who hasn't paid the entrance fee of five emeralds, get out!
dance.functions.dance.dj.villager.12: ] I hate thriller, it reminds me of the zombie invasions back home!
dance.functions.dance.dj.vindicator.6: ] I had to smash the DJ set with my axe. Sorry.
dance.functions.dance.dj.vindicator.12: ] Anyone like my leather jacket? No? Rip.
dance.functions.dance.dj.wither.3: ] It sucks whenever the two other heads start dating and I end up being the third wheel...
dance.functions.dance.dj.wither.6: ] I have no idea how I'm doing this DJ thing. I don't have any hands!
dance.functions.dance.dj.wither.9: ] BOOM! BOOM! BOOM! I know that's the creeper rap but I do booms too!
dance.functions.dance.dj.zombie.6: ] I'm the deadest DJ out there!
dance.functions.dance.dj.zombie.9: ] There's a zombie on the lawn!
dance.functions.dance.dj.zombie.12: ] My name is Jeff, and DJ stands for Dead Jeff!
